{"type":"message","id":"ca5b68bb","parentId":"62053241","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:30:37.729Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d4d1a46ad97947bd8cf9aac7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v8.45 - 设备设置记忆模块\n\n根据设备MAC保存/恢复各项参数配置。\n存储路径: data/devices/{mac}/settings.json\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_data_path_read, get_data_path_write\n\n\ndef load_settings(mac_clean: str) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"加载设备保存的设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: 设备设置，或 None 如果不存在\n    \"\"\"\n    path = get_data_path_read(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    if path and path.exists():\n        try:\n            with open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n                return json.load(f)\n        except Exception:\n            return None\n    return None\n\n\ndef save_settings(mac_clean: str, settings: dict[str, Any]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"保存设备设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        settings: 要保存的设置\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: 是否保存成功\n    \"\"\"\n    from datetime import datetime, timezone\n\n    # 合并现有设置\n    existing = load_settings(mac_clean) or {}\n    existing.update(settings)\n    existing['last_updated'] = datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat()\n\n    path = get_data_path_write(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    try:\n        with open(path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            json.dump(existing, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n        return True\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783272637729}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5a1775f","parentId":"ca5b68bb","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:31:12.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有完整的现状了：\n1. device_settings.py 只有两个函数：load_settings() 和 save_settings()\n2. save_settings 接受 mac_clean 和一个 dict\n3. 现有 router.py 中的保存调用在 `/image/settings` PUT 端点（line 1237-1264），保存的是 image_brightness, image_contrast, image_saturation\n\n老板的要求：\n1. 保存所有可操作的设置（除了PTZ运动控制和PTZ位置）\n2. 框选白平衡/对焦过程结束后执行一次保存\n3. router.py 只提供路由端点，保存逻辑在 device_settings.py 中完成\n4. 禁止硬编码 MAC/IP/型号\n5. 禁止改其他代码，禁止新脚本\n6. 备份 → 迭代版本号 → 分步执行\n\n我需要检查 router.py 中现有的保存调用位置（大约在 line 1237 附近），看看当前保存了什么，还缺什么。\n\n从 router.py 中：\n- `/image/settings` PUT: 只保存了 brightness/contrast/saturation\n- `/image/white-balance` PUT: 没有调用 save\n- `/whitebalance/auto` (router.py line 600-606): 没有保存\n\n等等，router.py 文件很长，我之前只看到了部分内容。让我查找 router.py 中所有调用 save_device_settings 的地方，以及所有 PUT 设置端点。\n\n我需要看 router.py 的 1237 行附近和其他相关端点。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在需要看 router.py 中现有的保存调用和所有 PUT 设置端点：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_db7364fd4951472f8f7d1706","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\api\\router.py -Pattern \"save_device_settings|save_settings\" | ForEach-Object { \"$($_.LineNumber): $($_.Line.Trim())\" }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":419,"cacheRead":37787,"cacheWrite":905,"totalTokens":39117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783272637730,"responseId":"msg_dbe9c400-762a-44bc-8200-d17922733721"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e75ae8d5","parentId":"e5a1775f","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:31:13.404Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_db7364fd4951472f8f7d1706","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"46: from src.advanced.device_settings import save_settings as save_device_settings, load_settings\r\n1440: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"image_settings\": updated})\r\n1763: async def save_settings() -> dict:\r\n2990: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"whitebalance\": {\"mode\": mode_val, \"red_gain\": red_val, \"blue_gain\": blue_val}})\r\n3093: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"noisereduce\": {\"spatial_level\": spatial, \"temporal_level\": temporal}})\r\n3251: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"exposure\": {\"mode\": mode}})\r\n3386: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"shutter\": {\"level\": level}})\r\n3465: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"iris\": {\"level\": level}})\r\n3613: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"sharpness\": {\"level\": level}})\r\n3819: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"slow_shutter\": {\"dss_level\": dss_level, \"enabled\": dss_level != \"off\"}})"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1106,"aggregated":"46: from src.advanced.device_settings import save_settings as save_device_settings, load_settings\r\n1440: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"image_settings\": updated})\r\n1763: async def save_settings() -> dict:\r\n2990: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"whitebalance\": {\"mode\": mode_val, \"red_gain\": red_val, \"blue_gain\": blue_val}})\r\n3093: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"noisereduce\": {\"spatial_level\": spatial, \"temporal_level\": temporal}})\r\n3251: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"exposure\": {\"mode\": mode}})\r\n3386: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"shutter\": {\"level\": level}})\r\n3465: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"iris\": {\"level\": level}})\r\n3613: save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"sharpness\": {\"level\": level}})\r\n3819: save_device_settings(mac_clea