{"type":"message","id":"320a44ad","parentId":"e72439e7","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:32:45.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the current state and understand what needs to be done:\n\n1. **Current save mechanism**: router.py already calls `save_device_settings()` after each PUT endpoint succeeds (whitebalance, noisereduce, exposure, shutter, iris, sharpness, slow_shutter, image_settings). This is the \"per-setting\" save.\n\n2. **The problem**: During whitebalance search (框选白平衡) and autofocus (框选对焦), the `run()` methods in `whitebalance.py` and `autofocus.py` call `_set_wb_gains()` and `_set_wb_mode()` directly via ISAPI - these calls bypass router.py's save logic. So the final R/B gains and modes after search completion are NOT saved.\n\n3. **What needs to be saved after search completion**:\n   - WhiteBalance: final R gain, B gain, mode (locked after completion)\n   - Autofocus: focus mode (manual after completion)\n\n4. **Constraints**:\n   - No new scripts\n   - Only modify what's absolutely needed\n   - Use existing `device_settings.py` for save/load\n   - router.py only provides routing\n   - Must backup before changes\n   - Must iterate version number\n   - Report any blockers immediately\n\nLet me read the relevant sections of router.py for the whitebalance_search and focus_search endpoints to understand the full flow.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e6163b72fd744417b48a3a73","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":150,"offset":4145,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/api/router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":39589,"output":365,"cacheRead":38272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78226,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783272752266,"responseId":"chatcmpl-58a9e6dc-8122-9d95-914d-69cfc7ce39cf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"552ed1d3","parentId":"320a44ad","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:32:45.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e6163b72fd744417b48a3a73","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    stats = _rgb_stats(bgr)\r\n    contrast = calc_contrast(bgr)\r\n    return {\"success\": True, \"crop\": info, \"rgb\": stats, \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2)}\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n# v8.41: 搜索器全局变量\r\n_wb_searcher = None\r\n_focus_searcher = None\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-search\", summary=\"白平衡迭代搜索 (SSE)\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def whitebalance_search(data: dict):\r\n    \"\"\"白平衡迭代搜索 - SSE流式。路由层只验证输入和调用白平衡模块。\"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from fastapi.responses import StreamingResponse\r\n    from src.controlpanel.whitebalance import WhiteBalanceSearcher\r\n\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': 'PTZ控制器未初始化'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    connected = mgr.get_connected_device()\r\n    if not connected:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '无活跃设备'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    device_ip = connected[\"ip\"]\r\n    client, err = _get_client_for_device(mgr, device_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': err})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    x = float(data.get(\"x\", 0))\r\n    y = float(data.get(\"y\", 0))\r\n    w = float(data.get(\"w\", 0))\r\n    h = float(data.get(\"h\", 0))\r\n\r\n    if w <= 0 or h <= 0:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '框选区域无效'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    searcher = WhiteBalanceSearcher(\r\n        mgr=mgr, device_ip=device_ip, client=client,\r\n        x=x, y=y, w=w, h=h,\r\n        capture_func=_capture_and_crop,\r\n        cleanup_func=_cleanup_temp\r\n    )\r\n    \r\n    # v8.41: 保存搜索器到全局变量\r\n    global _wb_searcher\r\n    _wb_searcher = searcher\r\n    \r\n    return StreamingResponse(\r\n        searcher.run(),\r\n        media_type=\"text/event-stream\",\r\n        headers={\"Cache-Control\": \"no-cache\", \"X-Accel-Buffering\": \"no\"}\r\n    )\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-stop\", summary=\"停止白平衡搜索\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def whitebalance_stop():\r\n    \"\"\"停止当前白平衡搜索并写入最佳值到设备\"\"\"\r\n    global _wb_searcher\r\n    if not _wb_searcher:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"无活跃的白平衡搜索\"}\r\n    \r\n    _wb_searcher._interrupt()\r\n    _wb_searcher = None\r\n    \r\n    return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"白平衡搜索已停止\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/focus-search\", summary=\"反差对焦搜索\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def focus_search(data: dict):\r\n    \"\"\"反差对焦搜索 - SSE流式。路由层只验证输入和调用对焦模块。\"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from fastapi.responses import StreamingResponse\r\n    from src.controlpanel.autofocus import FocusSearcher\r\n\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': 'PTZ控制器未初始化'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    connected = mgr.get_connected_device()\r\n    if not connected:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '无活跃设备'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    device_ip = connected[\"ip\"]\r\n    client, err = _get_client_for_device(mgr, device_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': err})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    x = float(data.get(\"x\", 0))\r\n    y = float(data.get(\"y\", 0))\r\n    w = float(data.get(\"w\", 0))\r\n    h = float(data.get(\"h\", 0))\r\n\r\n    if w <= 0 or h <= 0:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '框选区域无效'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    searcher = FocusSearcher(\r\n        mgr=mgr, device_ip=device_ip, client=client,\r\n        x=x, y=y, w=w, h=h,\r\n        capture_func=_capture_and_crop,\r\n        cleanup_func=_cleanup_temp\r\n    )\r\n    \r\n    # v8.41: 保存搜索器到全局变量\r\n    global _focus_searcher\r\n    _focus_searcher = searcher\r\n    \r\n    return StreamingResponse(\r\n        searcher.run(),\r\n        media_type=\"text/event-stream\",\r\n        headers={\"Cache-Control\": \"no-cache\", \"X-Accel-Buffering\": \"no\"}\r\n    )\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/focus-stop\", summary=\"停止对焦搜索\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def focus_stop():\r\n    \"\"\"停止当前对焦搜索\"\"\"\r\n    global _focus_searcher\r\n    if not _focus_searcher:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"无活跃的对焦搜索\"}\r\n    \r\n    _focus_searcher._interrupt()\r\n    _focus_searcher = None\r\n    \r\n\n[76 more lines in file. Use offset=4295 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783272765307}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee89f32b","parentId":"552ed1d3","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:33:32.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在对整个代码结构有了清晰的认识。让我分析当前状态和需要修复的问题：\n\n**当前状态：**\n1. `device_settings.py` 只有 `load_settings()` 和 `save_settings()` 两个基础函数\n2. `router.py` 中各个 PUT 端点在成功后调用 `save_device_settings()` 保存设置：\n   - 白平衡 (line 2990)\n   - 降噪 (line 3093)\n   - 曝光 (line 3251)\n   - 快门 (line 3386)\n   - 光圈 (line 3465)\n   - 锐化 (line 3613)\n   - 慢快门 (line 3819)\n   - 图像设置 (line 1440)\n\n3. `whitebalance.py` 的 `WhiteBalanceSearcher.run()` 在搜索过程中：\n   - 调用 `_set_wb_gains()` 多次（每步都通过 ISAPI PUT 设置增益）\n   - 结束时调用 `_set_wb_mode(\"locked\")`\n   - 但结束时**没有保存最终参数到 settings.json**\n\n4. `autofocus.py` 的 `FocusSearcher.run()` 在搜索过程中：\n   - 调用 `_set_manual_focus()` 开始\n   - 结束时移动焦点到最终位置\n   - 但结束时**没有保存对焦模式到 settings.json**\n\n5. 路由层的 `whitebalance_search` 和 `focus_search` 端点直接返回 `StreamingResponse(searcher.run())`，搜索结束后的参数不会触发 router 的 save 逻辑。\n\n**老板的需求分析：**\n\n需求1：保存整个主控台所有可操作设置的快照（除了手动PTZ运动控制和PTZ位置）\n- 这意味着需要一个\"全量快照\"功能，能读取设备当前所有参数并保存\n\n需求2：框选白平衡/对焦过程中有大量调用，需要结束时执行一次保存\n- 白平衡结束时：保存最终的 R/B 增益值和白平衡模式（locked）\n- 对焦结束时：保存对焦模式\n- 这些保存必须是异步的，不能阻塞 SSE 流\n\n需求3：禁止新脚本，只在现有条件下开发，禁止过度开发\n\n**老板的补充要求：**\n1. router.py 只提供端点路由，保存和读取由 device_settings.py 完成\n2. 禁止硬编码 MAC/IP/型号\n3. 只改必须改的部分\n4. 保存不包含图片，只包含最终定档的 R/B 白平衡数值、白平衡模式、对焦模式\n5. 备份 → 迭代版本号 → 分步执行 → 遇阻即停\n\n**修复计划：**\n\n### 第一步：修改 device_settings.py\n- 添加一个 `snapshot_device_settings()` 函数，负责：\n  - 接收 MAC 和设备参数 dict\n  - 合并保存到 settings.json（已有 `save_settings`）\n  - 或者更简单地：在现有基础上添加一个专门保存搜索完成后参数的函数\n\n### 第二步：修改 whitebalance.py\n- 在 `run()` 方法的 `done` 和 `interrupt` 分支中，搜索结束后调用 `save_settings()` 保存最终的 R/B 增益和白平衡模式\n\n### 第三步：修改 autofocus.py\n- 在 `run()` 方法的 `done` 分支中，搜索结束后保存对焦模式\n\n### 关键问题：如何获取 MAC？\n\n在 `WhiteBalanceSearcher` 和 `FocusSearcher` 中：\n- 有 `self.mgr` (PTZDeviceController)\n- 有 `self.device_ip`\n\n需要从 `mgr` 中根据 IP 找到 MAC。让我看看 PTZDeviceController 提供了什么方法。\n\n实际上，从 router.py 中可以看到，`mgr.get_connected_device()` 返回 `connected` dict，包含 `ip` 和可能的 `mac`。\n\n让我检查 `PTZDeviceController` 的实现，看看如何从 IP 获取 MAC。\n\n不过等等，老板说\"禁止开发新脚本，禁止引入新脚本，只允许在现有的条件下开发\"。\n\n最简单的方案：\n1. 在 router.py 创建 searcher 时，把 MAC 传进去\n2. 或者在 whitebalance.py/autofocus.py 中通过 mgr 查询 MAC\n\n让我看看 connected dict 包含什么。从 router.py 中 `connected = mgr.get_connected_device()` 后面 `device_ip = connected[\"ip\"]`。\n\n让我检查 PTZDeviceController 的 get_connected_device 方法。\n\n其实更简单的方案：在 router.py 的 whitebalance_search 和 focus_search 端点中，搜索是通过 SSE 流进行的。router.py 已经有 connected 设备的信息。\n\n但问题是 SSE 流结束后 router.py 的代码已经执行完了。所以需要在 searcher.run() 内部完成保存。\n\n方案：给 WhiteBalanceSearcher 和 FocusSearcher 传入 MAC 参数，在搜索结束时调用 save_settings。\n\n让我检查 mgr 是否有方法从 IP 获取 MAC。\n\n实际上，从 router.py 中已经能看到：\n- `_resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)` 可以反向解析\n- `mgr.list_stored_devices()` 可以列出所有设备\n- `mgr.get_discovered_devices()` 可以发现设备\n\n所以可以从 mgr 中根据 IP 找到 MAC。\n\n或者更简单：在 router.py 创建 searcher 时，把 connected dict 中的 mac 传给 searcher。\n\n让我看看 connected dict 有没有 mac。\n\n我需要检查 PTZDeviceController.get_connected_device() 返回什么。\n\n让我搜索一下。\n\n算了，我不需要看所有代码。根据老板的要求，我应该：\n\n1. 先备份\n2. 迭代版本号\n3. 分步执行\n4. 遇阻即停\n\n让我先做以下分析：\n\n**需要保存的参数（搜索结束后）：**\n- 白平衡：mode=locked, red_gain=X, blue_gain=Y\n- 对焦：focus_mode=MANUAL (或者不保存对焦模式？对焦只是搜索最终位置，对焦模式在开始时设置为 MANUAL)\n\n等等，老板说\"只包含运行完毕之后，定档的R B白平衡数值、白平衡模式、对焦模式\"。\n\n所以保存内容：\n- 白平衡结束后：wb mode=locked, red_gain, blue_gain\n- 对焦结束后：focus mode\n\n**修改方案（最小化）：**\n\n1. **device_settings.py**: 不需要新增函数，现有 `save_settings()` 已经够用\n\n2. **whitebalance.py**: \n   - 构造函数增加 `mac_clean` 参数\n   - `run()` 结束时（done/interrupt 分支）调用 `save_settings(mac_clean, {\"whitebalance\": {...}})`\n\n3. **autofocus.py**:\n   - 构造函数增加 `mac_clean` 参数\n   - `run()` 结束时调用 `save_settings(mac_clean, {\"focus\": {\"mode\": \"manual\"}})`\n\n4. **router.py**:\n   - 在 whitebalance_search 和 focus_search 端点中，获取 MAC 并传给 searcher\n\n等等，但是 router.py 中创建 searcher 时，需要获取 MAC。当前 connected dict 中有 mac 吗？\n\n让我检查 get_connected_device 返回什么。\n\n实际上，我可以用另一种方式：从 mgr.list_stored_devices() 中根据 IP 找到 MAC。或者从 discovered_devices 中找。\n\n但最简单的方案是：在 router.py 中，connected = mgr.get_connected_device()，connected dict 很可能包含 mac。\n\n让我检查 PTZDeviceController 的 get_connected_device 方法。\n\n我搜索一下相关文件。\n\n算了，让我用另一个方案：在 router.py 中，根据 device_ip 从 mgr 的设备列表中查找 MAC，然后传给 searcher。\n\n让我直接开始分步执行。\n\n**Step 0: 备份**\n**Step 1: 检查 connected dict 是否包含 mac**\n**Step 2: 修改 whitebalance.py - 添加保存逻辑**\n**Step 3: 修改 autofocus.py - 添加保存逻辑**\n**Step 4: 修改 router.py - 传 MAC 给 searcher**\n**Step 5: 迭代版本号**\n\n先开始备份。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现状分析完成。制定修复计划：\n\n**问题**：白平衡/对焦搜索结束后，最终参数未保存到 settings.json。搜索过程中 searcher 直接通过 ISAPI PUT 操作设备，绕过了 router 的 save 逻辑。\n\n**修复范围（最小化）**：\n1. `whitebalance.py` — run() 结束时保存 R/B 增益 + WB 模式\n2. `autofocus.py` — run() 结束时保存对焦模式\n3. `router.py` — 创建 searcher 时传入 MAC\n\n开始执行。**Step 0: 备份**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_075d43330203407f91369b36","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"backup_20260706_0129\" -Force | Out-Null; Copy-Item -Path src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py, src\\controlpanel\\autofocus.py, src\\advanced\\device_settings.py, src\\api\\router.py, src\\main\\constants.py -Destination \"backup_20260706_0129\\\" -Force; Get-ChildItem backup_20260706_0129\\ | ForEach-Object { $_.Name }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":2052,"cacheRead":39370,"cacheWrite":6907,"totalTokens":48335,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783272765308,"responseId":"msg_bb72d386-df32-465c-bf54-a8344f9ac28d"}}
