{"type":"message","id":"46a932df","parentId":"9f48abbe","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:34:56.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough info to execute the fix. Let me analyze:\n\n**Current state:**\n1. `router.py` line 996-1005 has a PUT endpoint for focus configuration that sets focusStyle but does NOT call `save_device_settings`\n2. `whitebalance.py` `WhiteBalanceSearcher.run()` sets WB mode to \"locked\" at end but does NOT save to settings.json\n3. `autofocus.py` `FocusSearcher.run()` sets focus to MANUAL at start but does NOT save at end\n4. `get_connected_device()` returns `connected[\"mac\"]` which is the MAC\n5. `save_settings(mac_clean, dict)` already exists in device_settings.py\n\n**What needs to change:**\n1. `whitebalance.py`: Add `mac_clean` param to constructor, call `save_settings()` after run() completes (both done and interrupt paths) with final R/B gains + WB mode\n2. `autofocus.py`: Add `mac_clean` param to constructor, call `save_settings()` after run() completes with focus mode\n3. `router.py`: Pass `mac_clean` to searcher constructors in `whitebalance_search()` and `focus_search()` endpoints\n4. Add focus mode save to the focus PUT endpoint in router.py (line ~1005) - wait, boss said \"只修复绝对需求的部分\". Let me think about this...\n\nActually, boss said:\n- \"保存设备当前配置，是整个astrohub主控台上所有设置的快照\" - save ALL settings\n- \"保存中，需要异步，需要降低占用，在画面控制-区域，也就是框选白平衡和框选自动对焦的时候，过程中有大量的调用，我需要在整个对焦或白平衡结束之后，执行一次保存\"\n- \"保存工作不包含任何图片，只包含运行完毕之后，定档的R B白平衡数值、白平衡模式、对焦模式\"\n\nSo the save after search completion should include:\n- For WB: R gain, B gain, WB mode (locked)\n- For focus: focus mode (manual)\n\nAnd the existing save calls in router.py for other settings (whitebalance PUT, noisereduce PUT, etc.) are already working correctly - those are user-initiated changes through the UI, not during search.\n\nThe fix needed:\n1. **whitebalance.py**: Pass MAC, save after search ends (done + interrupt paths)\n2. **autofocus.py**: Pass MAC, save after search ends\n3. **router.py**: Pass `connected[\"mac\"]` to both searcher constructors\n\nThat's it - minimal changes. No new scripts, no device_settings.py changes needed (save_settings already works).\n\nWait, I also need to check: does the focus PUT endpoint in router.py need a save call? Let me check line 996-1005 more carefully.\n\nLooking at the search results, line 996 has `# ISAPI 端点: PUT /ISAPI/Image/channels/1/focusConfiguration` - this is likely in a comment block or an actual endpoint. Let me check if this endpoint already has save_device_settings or not.\n\nFrom my earlier scan of all save_device_settings calls:\n- Line 1440: image_settings\n- Line 2990: whitebalance\n- Line 3093: noisereduce\n- Line 3251: exposure\n- Line 3386: shutter\n- Line 3465: iris\n- Line 3613: sharpness\n- Line 3819: slow_shutter\n\nFocus is NOT in the list. So the focus PUT endpoint doesn't save either.\n\nBut boss said \"只修复绝对需求的部分和依赖的部分\". The focus PUT endpoint save is needed for the \"complete snapshot\" requirement. Let me add it.\n\nActually wait - let me re-read boss's requirements:\n\"保存设备当前配置，是整个astrohub主控台上所有设置的快照\"\n\nThe focus PUT endpoint should also save. And the focus endpoint currently doesn't. Let me check what's at line 996-1010.\n\nI need to read that section of router.py.\n\nActually, let me focus on the immediate requirements:\n1. whitebalance search end → save R/B + mode\n2. autofocus search end → save focus mode  \n3. router.py pass MAC to searchers\n\nThe focus PUT endpoint save is a separate issue that already existed before. Boss said \"只修复绝对需求的部分\" - the absolute need right now is the search completion saves.\n\nBut wait, boss also said \"需要完整修复所有的关联\". So the focus PUT endpoint should also save. Let me read that section.\n\nLet me proceed step by step. First the search completion saves, then check if focus PUT needs save too.\n\nActually, I should also check: does the router.py have a dedicated focus mode PUT endpoint? Let me read around line 996.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在情况明确了。让我读取 focus PUT 端点的完整代码：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6574862643eb42849e98da27","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":980,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/api/router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1142,"cacheRead":50219,"cacheWrite":250,"totalTokens":51617,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783272872211,"responseId":"msg_9772fda4-e0b8-4ce2-a809-00ed275c444d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a08d89c9","parentId":"46a932df","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:34:56.757Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_6574862643eb42849e98da27","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"async def set_focus_mode(device_id: str, req: FocusModeRequest) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置对焦模式(手动/自动/半自动)\"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    # 调用 ISAPI 设置对焦模式\r\n    ctrl = mgr._controllers.get(target_ip)\r\n    if not ctrl:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"设备未连接\"}\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        # ISAPI 端点: PUT /ISAPI/Image/channels/1/focusConfiguration\r\n        mode_upper = \"MANUAL\" if req.mode.lower() == \"manual\" else (\"AUTO\" if req.mode.lower() == \"auto\" else \"SEMIAUTOMATIC\")\r\n\r\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<FocusConfiguration version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <focusStyle>{mode_upper}</focusStyle>\r\n  <focusLimited>300</focusLimited>\r\n</FocusConfiguration>'''\r\n\r\n        result = ctrl.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/focusConfiguration\", xml)\r\n\r\n        if result.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"ptz\", \"focus_mode\", {\"device\": device_id, \"mode\": req.mode})\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"对焦模式已设置为 {req.mode}\"}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置对焦模式失败: {result.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置对焦模式失败: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/focus/mode\", summary=\"获取对焦模式\", tags=[\"PTZ\"])\r\nasync def get_focus_mode(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取当前对焦模式\"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl = mgr._controllers.get(target_ip)\r\n    if not ctrl:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"设备未连接\"}\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n        result = ctrl.client.get(\"/Image/channels/1\")\r\n        if result.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取图像配置失败: {result.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(result.xml)\r\n        focus_style = \"unknown\"\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            if elem.tag.endswith('focusStyle'):\r\n\n[3331 more lines in file. Use offset=1040 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783272896757}}
{"type":"message","id":"74e48da2","parentId":"a08d89c9","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:35:49.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有了完整的情况：\n\n**当前状态：**\n1. `router.py` 中的 `set_focus_mode` 端点 (line ~980-1016) 设置对焦模式后**没有调用** `save_device_settings`\n2. `whitebalance.py` 的 `WhiteBalanceSearcher.run()` 搜索完成后**没有保存**最终 R/B 增益和模式\n3. `autofocus.py` 的 `FocusSearcher.run()` 搜索完成后**没有保存**对焦模式\n4. `device_settings.py` 的 `save_settings()` 已经存在且工作正常\n\n**老板的需求：**\n1. 保存所有可操作设置的快照（除了PTZ运动控制和PTZ位置）\n2. 框选白平衡/对焦结束后执行一次保存\n3. 异步、低占用\n4. 禁止新脚本，禁止过度开发\n5. router.py只提供路由，保存由device_settings.py完成\n6. 禁止硬编码MAC/IP/型号\n7. 备份→迭代版本号→分步执行\n\n**修复计划（最小化）：**\n\n1. **whitebalance.py**: \n   - 构造函数增加 `mac_clean` 参数\n   - `run()` 结束时（done和interrupt分支）调用 `save_settings(mac_clean, {\"whitebalance\": {...}})`\n\n2. **autofocus.py**:\n   - 构造函数增加 `mac_clean` 参数  \n   - `run()` 结束时调用 `save_settings(mac_clean, {\"focus\": {\"mode\": \"manual\"}})`\n\n3. **router.py**:\n   - `set_focus_mode` 端点成功时添加 `save_device_settings` 调用\n   - `whitebalance_search` 端点传入 `mac_clean=connected[\"mac\"]`\n   - `focus_search` 端点传入 `mac_clean=connected[\"mac\"]`\n\n等等，让我再想想。老板说\"router.py只提供端点的路由。保存和读取的具体工作由device_settings.py完成\"。\n\n这意味着 router.py 中已经有 save_device_settings 调用是合理的（路由层调用保存函数），但保存逻辑本身在 device_settings.py 中。\n\n现在 router.py 中已经有这些调用模式：\n```python\nsave_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"whitebalance\": {\"mode\": mode_val, \"red_gain\": red_val, \"blue_gain\": blue_val}})\n```\n\n这是合理的模式。问题是：\n1. `set_focus_mode` 端点缺少保存调用\n2. `whitebalance_search` 和 `focus_search` 搜索完成后缺少保存\n\n让我重新审视：\n\n**需要修改的文件：**\n\n1. **router.py** (3处修改):\n   - `set_focus_mode` (line ~1006): 成功后添加 save_device_settings\n   - `whitebalance_search` (line ~4196): 传入 mac_clean\n   - `focus_search` (line ~4267): 传入 mac_clean\n\n2. **whitebalance.py** (2处修改):\n   - `__init__`: 增加 mac_clean 参数\n   - `run()`: done 和 interrupt 分支添加保存\n\n3. **autofocus.py** (2处修改):\n   - `__init__`: 增加 mac_clean 参数\n   - `run()`: