{"type":"message","id":"0339e769","parentId":"5f97a34b","timestamp":"2026-07-05T17:41:32.751Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\n从日志看，AstroHub 启动失败的原因是端口 10280 被占用（WinError 10048）。这是因为之前已经有一个 AstroHub 实例在运行。\n\n这是一个正常的情况——之前的服务已经在运行，所以新启动的失败了。这不影响我提交的修改报告。\n\n我应该告诉老板这个情况，但不需要打扰他，除非他要求我重启服务。目前修改报告已经提交，等待审批。旧服务仍在端口 10280 运行。\n旧版本 AstroHub 已在端口 10280 运行，新进程因端口冲突退出。这是正常现象，不影响 v8.47 修改。修改已就绪，等待老板审批后重启服务即可生效。**旧 AstroHub 进程仍在运行（端口 10280），新进程启动失败。**\n\n这是正常的——修改已就绪，待老板审批后重启服务即可生效。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The old AstroHub process exited with code 1 because port 10280 is already in use by the existing running AstroHub instance. This is expected behavior - the old process I started was the pre-modification version, and it couldn't bind to the port because the current AstroHub is already running.\n\nThe important thing is that all 4 modified files have passed Python syntax validation:\n- whitebalance.py ✅\n- autofocus.py ✅\n- router.py ✅\n- constants.py ✅\n\nThe modifications are complete. The user asked me to report and wait for approval. The old process exit is just background noise - it's not relevant to the user since they haven't asked me to start the new version yet.\n\nI should not relay this to the user. The exec completion is internal and not requested.旧版本 AstroHub 启动失败（端口 10280 已被占用），这是预期的——现有 AstroHub 实例正在运行。\n\n**v8.47 修改已全部完成，语法验证通过。** 等待老板审批后执行测试。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":422,"cacheRead":71643,"cacheWrite":1799,"totalTokens":73870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783273280523,"responseId":"msg_da8116ec-f97b-4cee-9869-57b44ecb1195"}}
