{"type":"message","id":"d9d68ae6","parentId":"ce5cc9da","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:03:44.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that I restored all the changes to the main control console. They want me to find the previous backup and compare the differences in OSD PTZ info switch and region analysis parts.\n\nLet me understand what happened:\n1. I made some modifications to restore v8.47 (added save_settings for whitebalance/autofocus/focus)\n2. The user is saying I accidentally restored/reverted some previous changes\n3. They want me to find the backup and compare differences\n\nThe backups I made were:\n- backup_20260706_0032 (first backup before my changes)\n- backup_20260706_0129 (backup I made during this session)\n\nThe backup_20260706_0032 contains the state BEFORE my v8.47 changes. The current files have my v8.47 changes.\n\nWait, let me re-read. The user says \"你给我把主控台的哪些修改都还原回来了\" - meaning \"you restored all the modifications to the main console\". This suggests I may have overwritten some files.\n\nLooking at the backup structure:\n- backup_20260706_0032\\src\\ contains all the source files\n- backup_20260706_0129\\src\\ contains all the source files\n\nThe user is asking me to compare the current files with the previous backups to see what OSD PTZ info switch and region analysis changes were made/lost.\n\nLet me compare:\n1. Current router.py vs backup_20260706_0032\\src\\api\\router.py\n2. Current console.html vs backup_20260706_0032\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\n\nThe user mentioned OSD PTZ and region analysis (框选分析). Let me check these specific files.\nThe output shows no files found in backup_20260706_0032\\src. This is strange. Let me check if the backup directory exists and what's in it.老板说我把主控台的修改都还原了。需要对比当前文件和之前备份的差异，特别是OSD PTZ信息开关和框选分析部分。但 backup_20260706_0032\\src 是空的，让我检查备份目录结构：\nThe user is saying that I restored the changes to the main console. They want me to compare the differences between the current files and the previous backup, specifically for OSD PTZ info switch and region analysis parts.\n\nLet me first understand what happened:\n1. I made modifications to add v8.47 features (whitebalance/autofocus save on search completion, focus mode save, etc.)\n2. The user is saying that I \"restored\" the modifications, which means I might have overwritten files with old backups\n3. They want me to compare the current files with the previous backup (backup_20260706_0032) to see what changed\n\nLooking at the command output:\n- `backup_20260706_0032` was a backup I made earlier (before v8.47 changes)\n- The user is saying I should compare the current state with that backup to see what was \"restored\"\n\nWait, I think I misunderstood. Let me re-read the message:\n\"卧槽你大爷的，你给我把主控台的哪些修改都还原回来了？找到之前备份，修改OSD PTZ信息开关、修改框选分析的部分，完全对比异同！\"\n\nTranslation: \"F*** you, did you restore all the modifications to the main console? Find the previous backup, the parts that modified OSD PTZ info switch and region analysis, compare them completely!\"\n\nSo the user is saying that I (in a previous session or action) restored/overwrote some modifications to the main console. They want me to:\n1. Find the previous backup\n2. Compare the current state with the backup for OSD PTZ info switch and region analysis parts\n\nLet me check what the backup_20260706_0032 contains. The output shows no files were found, which means the directory might be empty or the path is wrong.\n\nLet me check the backup directories:\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_f6b4e25b28614431aa3202b8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && Get-ChildItem -Path backup_20260706_0032\\src -Directory | ForEach-Object { $_.Name }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1009,"cacheRead":17590,"cacheWrite":63983,"totalTokens":82588,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReaso