{"type":"message","id":"fd8d743a","parentId":"7dae14f6","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:04:46.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that I restored the changes to the main console. Let me analyze what happened:\n\n1. The console.html comparison shows `Count: 0` - meaning current console.html is IDENTICAL to backup_20260706_0032\n2. The router.py comparison shows only my v8.47 changes (focus mode save, mac_clean passing)\n\nBut the user is saying I \"restored\" modifications. This is confusing because:\n- The current files match the backup_20260706_0032\n- But the user says I restored modifications\n\nWait, let me re-read: \"你给我把主控台的哪些修改都还原回来了？\" means \"What changes to the main console did you restore?\"\n\nThe user is asking me to FIND OUT what was restored. They want me to compare the current state with a previous backup to identify what was lost/restored.\n\nLet me check if there's a newer backup than backup_20260706_0032 that might have had changes before I overwrote them. Or maybe the user is asking me to compare with a backup from an earlier version.\n\nLooking at the backup list:\n- backup_v826_rmse_20260703_151400\n- backup_v824_final_20260703_121100\n- backup_v822_fix_20260703_113300\n- backup_v821_hyperbola_20260703_102600\n- backup_v820_parabola_20260703_095800\n- backup_v815_wb_lock_20260703_052607\n- backup_v814_focus_20260703_051112\n- backup_v810_20260702_182831\n- backup_20260706_0129 (my first backup)\n- backup_20260706_0032 (my second backup)\n- backup_20260701_054251\n\nWait, the timestamps are confusing. backup_20260706_0032 is from 00:32, and backup_20260706_0129 is from 01:29. So backup_20260706_0032 is EARLIER than backup_20260706_0129.\n\nBut the user is saying I \"restored\" something. Maybe they're asking me to check if the current state matches the latest backup, or if there were changes between backups that got lost.\n\nLet me check backup_20260706_0129 to see what was there before I made my v8.47 changes. Wait, I created backup_20260706_0129 right before my edits, so it should be the \"before\" state.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The user is saying \"修改OSD PTZ信息开关、修改框选分析的部分\" - these are specific features they want me to check. They think I restored (overwrote) these features.\n\nBut from my comparison:\n1. router.py: Only v8.47 changes are different\n2. console.html: IDENTICAL to backup\n\nSo either:\n1. The user is mistaken\n2. Or the changes were made in a different backup period\n\nLet me check if there are differences between backup_20260706_0129 and backup_20260706_0032. Maybe there were changes between these two backups that got lost.\n\nWait, I need to be more careful. Let me check what files are in backup_20260706_0129 and compare them with the current state. The user might be referring to changes made between 20260706_0032 and 20260706_0129 that I overwrote.\n\nLet me list the files in backup_20260706_0129 and compare.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"...\nconsole.html 对比结果是 Count: 0，说明当前版本和 backup_20260706_0032 完全一致。\n\n但老板说我把修改还原了，可能是指在 backup_20260706_0032 和 backup_20260706_0129 之间有修改被我覆盖了。让我检查这两个备份之间的差异：老板说修改被还原了，但 router.py 和 console.html 对比显示没有差异。可能是 backup_20260706_0032 和 backup_20260706_0129 之间有差异。让我检查：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:91","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && Get-ChildItem backup_20260706_0129\\ -Recurse | ForEach-Object { $_.FullName.Replace(\"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\backup_20260706_0129\\\", \"\") }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":78913,"output":938,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79851,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783274660648,"responseId":"cht000d94e4@dx19f3373eeff2872503"}}
