{"type":"message","id":"7f71d734","parentId":"dcd6fc06","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:05:27.790Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板说\"你把主控台的哪些修改都还原回来了？\" - 意思是有人把之前的修改还原了。\n\n让我分析：\n1. backup_20260706_0032 - 包含完整的 src 目录结构\n2. backup_20260706_0129 - 只包含5个文件：autofocus.py, constants.py, device_settings.py, router.py, whitebalance.py\n\n时间线：\n- 2026-07-06 00:32 - 创建了 backup_20260706_0032（完整备份）\n- 2026-07-06 01:29 - 创建了 backup_20260706_0129（只备份了5个修改的文件）\n\n从命令历史看：\n1. 第一次会话中，老板要求备份当前修改，我做了 backup_20260706_0032\n2. 第二次会话中，老板要求备份后迭代版本号，我做了 backup_20260706_0129\n\n对比结果：\n- router.py: 只有v8.47的差异（我添加的focus保存和mac_clean传递）\n- console.html: Count: 0，说明当前版本和 backup_20260706_0032 完全一致\n\n这意味着：\n1. console.html 没有被修改\n2. router.py 只有v8.47的修改\n\n老板说\"修改OSD PTZ信息开关、修改框选分析的部分\" - 这些修改在哪里？\n\n让我检查：\n- backup_20260706_0032 中的 router.py 是否有 OSD/框选分析的功能？\n- 当前 router.py 是否也有？\n\n从之前的命令输出看，两个文件都有：\n- OSD相关函数（ptz_osd_toggle, ptz_osd_ptz_toggle, ptz_osd_info_toggle等）\n- 框选分析相关（vision/region-analyze）\n\n所以这些功能都存在，没有被还原。\n\n但老板说\"还原回来了\"，可能是指：\n1. 有人从 backup_20260706_0032 恢复了文件\n2. 或者之前的修改没有保存到正确的地方\n\n让我检查 backup_20260706_0032 和 backup_20260706_0129 之间的差异。如果 backup_20260706_0129 是新做的备份，它应该包含 backup_20260706_0032 之后的所有修改。\n\n但 backup_20260706_0129 只有5个文件，这说明：\n1. 可能只有这5个文件被修改\n2. 或者备份不完整\n\n让我对比 backup_20260706_0032 和 backup_20260706_0129 中的 router.py，看看是否有差异。\nbackup_20260706_0032 是完整备份，backup_20260706_0129 只有5个修改的文件。让我对比这两个备份中的 router.py，看是否有差异：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_74ec6dddcfd14e809148eab4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && Compare-Object (Get-Content backup_20260706_0032\\src\\api\\router.py -Encoding UTF8) (Get-Content backup_20260706_0129\\router.py -Encoding UTF8) | ForEach-Object { $_.SideIndicator + \" \" + $_.InputObject.Trim() } | Select-Object -First 30"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe user is saying I \"restored\" (还原) the modifications to the main control console. They want me to find the previous backup and compare the differences.\n\nLooking at the backups:\n1. backup_20260706_0032 - my first backup (before v8.47 changes)\n2. backup_20260706_0129 - my second backup (after v8.47 changes)\n\nThe user is asking me to compare the current files with the previous backup to see what OSD PTZ info switch and region analysis changes were made.\n\nLet me check what files are in backup_20260706_0032 vs backup_20260706_0129:\n\nbackup_20260706_0032 contains:\n- src\\api\\router.py\n- src\\advanced\\device_settings.py\n- src\\main\\constants.py\n- src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py\n- src\\controlpanel\\autofocus.py\n\nbackup_20260706_0129 contains:\n- autofocus.py\n- constants.py\n- device_settings.py\n- router.py\n- whitebalance.py\n\nWait, backup_20260706_0032 has subdirectory structure (src\\...), while backup_20260706_0129 is flat. Let me check the flat backup more carefully.\n\nActually, the user is saying I \"restored\" the modifications. This means they think I might have overwritten newer changes with older backup files. They want me to compare:\n1. Current files vs backup_20260706_0032 (which has the src structure)\n2. Specifically looking for OSD PTZ info switch and region analysis changes\n\nLet me compare the current router.py with backup_20260706_0032's router.py to see if there are any differences related to OSD PTZ or region analysis.\n\nFrom the earlier output, the router.py comparison showed:\n- Line 1144: OSD PTZ template in current\n- Line 1137: OSD PTZ template in backup\n\nThe line numbers are different! This suggests the files have different content. Let me do a more detailed comparison.\n\nAlso, I need to check the console.html and other files for OSD PTZ and region analysis changes.\n\nLet me compare the key files more thoroughly.备份_20260706_0129 只有 5 个文件（扁平结构）。让我详细对比 backup_20260706_0032（完整备份）和当前文件的 OSD PTZ 和框选分析部分：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_db26f3cc0efb4febbf320d36","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd as