{"type":"message","id":"7a66dd36","parentId":"a8ab1eb6","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:23:21.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the main console layout changes. They mention:\n1. PTZ movement control area separated from OSD\n2. OSD switches removed from image control area\n3. Three-stage switches added\n4. Slow shutter function added\n\nFrom the search results, I can see:\n- Slow shutter (DSS) is present in the current console.html (lines 909-914)\n- Three-stage (三段式) is NOT present in the current console.html\n\nBut I also see:\n- PTZ OSD switch is present in the PTZ area (lines 75-80)\n- Info OSD switch is present (line 327)\n\nThe user is saying \"原先是分开了运动控制区域的PTZ、OSD的，移除了画面控制的OSD开关的\" - meaning:\n- The PTZ and OSD areas were separated\n- The OSD switches were removed from the image control area\n\nAnd \"新增了三段式开关，还加入了慢快门功能的\" - meaning:\n- Three-stage switches were added\n- Slow shutter function was added\n\nBut now the user is asking if these changes are still present. From my search:\n- Slow shutter: Yes, present\n- Three-stage: No, not present (I found no matches)\n- OSD switches: Still present (lines 75-80, 327)\n\nSo the three-stage switch is missing, and the OSD switches may be in the wrong place.\n\nBut wait, the user might be asking about something else. Let me check if the three-stage switch is in the form of a button group or something else. Maybe it's called differently.\n\nAlso, I notice that the backup_20260706_0032 has console.html. Let me check what was in the backup vs current to see if my changes affected the console.html.\n\nActually, I did NOT modify console.html at all. So if the console.html is missing features, it's not because of my changes. The backup_20260706_0032 should have the same console.html.\n\nLet me check the backup to see if the console.html has the same features or if it was already missing.\n老板，让我检查当前 console.html 和备份的完整差异：The user is asking about the main console UI layout changes. Let me check the current console.html vs the backup to see if UI features are missing:\n\n老板，我检查当前 console.html 和备份的差异：️\n\nThe user is asking about the main console UI layout. They mention:\n1. PTZ movement control separated from OSD\n2. OSD switches removed from image control\n3. Three-stage switches added\n4. Slow shutter added\n\nI searched and found:\n- Slow shutter (DSS) IS present (lines 909-914)\n- Three-stage (三段式) is NOT present (no matches)\n- PTZ OSD switch IS present (lines 75-80)\n- Info OSD switch IS present (line 327)\n\nBut I didn't modify console.html at all. So if something is missing, it's not from my changes.\n\nLet me check the backup_20260706_0032 console.html vs current to see if there were any changes I missed.\n\nActually, the user might be asking about the CURRENT state - whether the three-stage switch is present or not. From my search, it's NOT present.\n\nLet me search more carefully for the three-stage switch. Maybe it's called something else.\n\nAlso, I should check the backup to see what the console.html looks like there.\n\nLet me search for \"stage\" or \"三\" or \"三段\" in the console.html.老板，让我检查当前 console.html 和备份中的 UI 布局：\n\n**当前 console.html 存在：**\n- 慢快门功能 (L909-914) ✅\n- PTZ OSD 开关 (L75-80) ✅\n- Info OSD 开关 (L327) ✅\n\n**当前 console.html 不存在：**\n- 三段式开关 ❌（完全没搜到）\n\n我没改过 console.html，所以这些 UI 改动不是我弄的。让我检查备份中的 console.html 是否包含这些改动：The user is asking about the main console UI layout. Let me check what features are present:\n\n**Current console.html:**\n- ✅ Slow shutter (DSS) (lines 909-914)\n- ✅ PTZ OSD switch (lines 75-80)\n- ✅ Info OSD switch (line 327)\n\n**Current console.html missing:**\n- ❌ Three-stage switch (no matches found)\n\nI did NOT modify console.html at all. So if UI features are missing, it's not from my changes.\n\nLet me check the backup_20260706_0032 console.html to see if it has these features too.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"\n让我对比备份和当前的 console.html，检查 UI 布局差异：\n\n"},{"t