{"type":"message","id":"0ad5c442","parentId":"bd8329c1","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:41:07.293Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"7 月 5 日的备份都没有 console.html 文件。这些备份只包含了部分文件（如 region_analyzer.py 等）。\n\n我需要找另一个策略。老板说\"添加了慢快门的版本也恢复没了\"。这说明之前有一个版本是包含慢快门 HTML 的。\n\n让我搜索所有备份目录，看看有没有哪个包含 console.html 并且有慢快门功能。\n\n当前情况：\n- 当前 src/web/includes/console.html (87741 bytes) 只有 JS 引用，没有 HTML 元素\n- 7 月 5 日的备份都没有 console.html\n- 7 月 3 日的备份 (backup_20260706_0032) 有 console.html 但也只有 JS 引用\n\n我需要找更早的备份，或者检查是否有其他地方存储了正确的版本。\n\n让我搜索所有 backup 目录中的 console.html。\n让我搜索所有备份目录中的 console.html：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bb4b5dbdf9b747a3a16f28f4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\" -Recurse -Filter \"console.html\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { $_.FullName -like \"*backup*\" } | ForEach-Object { \"$($_.FullName): $($_.Length) bytes, $($_.LastWriteTime)\" }"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_67614a5d29d74c41b4509e20","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\" -Recurse -Filter \"console.html\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-String -Pattern \"slowShutterSelect\" -SimpleMatch | ForEach-Object { \"$($_.Path | Split-Path -Parent | Split-Path -Parent): HTML element found\" }"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe user is saying I mistakenly restored something that was already removed. They're asking me to find the version before v8.45 that has the slow shutter feature in the main console UI.\n\nFrom the HEARTBEAT.md, I can see that:\n- v8.45 added slow shutter migration to DSS\n- v8.46 added device parameter memory\n\nThe user mentioned:\n1. The original layout separated PTZ movement control area from OSD\n2. Removed OSD switches from image control area\n3. Added three-stage switches\n4. Added slow shutter functionality\n\nLet me check the backup directories more carefully. The backups from July 5th are in the parent directory (C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\), not in astrohub.\n\nLet me look for console.html files in those backup directories.\n让我检查 7 月 5 日备份目录中的 console.html，找到包含慢快门功能的版本：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_423fd744d02d40e68d598168","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\backup_20260705_*\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | ForEach-Object { \"$($_.Directory.Name): $($_.Length) bytes\" }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":707,"cacheRead":137626,"cacheWrite":25085,"totalTokens":163424,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783276847922,"responseId":"msg_316321f5-9cba-4bec-9ebe-12784ea8f54f"}}
