{"type":"message","id":"2738168f","parentId":"44529b48","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:43:07.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the differences. The backup_20260705_205538 version (98047 bytes, from July 5) has:\n\n1. **Slow shutter HTML element** (line 99): `<select id=\"slowShutterSelect\"...>` ✅\n2. **Slow shutter JS functions** (lines 1549, 1550, 1598, 2015-2016): loadSlowShutter, setSlowShutter ✅\n3. **Info OSD and PTZ OSD switches** in the image control area (lines 84, 91) - these are toggle switches\n4. **toggle-switch CSS** (lines 380, 386) ✅\n\nThe current console.html (87741 bytes) has:\n- **NO slow shutter HTML element** (only JS references)\n- **PTZ OSD in motion control area** (line 75-80: `ptzOsdSwitchInPtz`)\n- **Info OSD in image control area** (line 320-327: `infoOsdSwitch`)\n\nThe key difference: The backup_20260705_205538 version has BOTH `infoOsdSwitch` and `ptzOsdSwitch` in the image control area (lines 84, 91), while the current version has `ptzOsdSwitchInPtz` in the motion control area and `infoOsdSwitch` in the image control area.\n\nWait, let me re-read. The user said:\n- \"原先是分开了运动控制区域的PTZ、OSD的\" - originally PTZ and OSD were separated in the motion control area\n- \"移除了画面控制的OSD开关的\" - removed OSD switches from image control area\n- \"新增了三段式开关\" - added three-stage switches\n- \"加入了慢快门功能的\" - added slow shutter function\n\nSo the user is saying the previous version:\n1. Had PTZ and OSD separated in the motion control area\n2. Removed OSD switches from image control area\n3. Added three-stage switches\n4. Added slow shutter function\n\nBut looking at the backup_20260705_205538, it seems to have BOTH infoOsdSwitch (line 84) and ptzOsdSwitch (line 91) in what appears to be the image control area. This doesn't match what the user described.\n\nLet me look more carefully at the layout structure of the backup. The toggle switches (lines 83-91) might be in the image control area or somewhere else. I need to check the surrounding context.\n\nActually, looking at line 598: \"v7.11: 禁止用户自定义控制(画面控制区 OSD 开关,与运动控制区)\" and line 673: \"v7.11: 禁止用户自定义控制开关（画面控制区 OSD 开关，与运动控制区）\"\n\nThis suggests the backup_20260705_205538 version has OSD switches in the image control area. But the user said they were REMOVED from the image control area.\n\nWait, I think I'm misunderstanding. Let me re-read the user's message:\n\"我是说，整个主控台界面的布局，原先是分开了运动控制区域的PTZ、OSD的，移除了画面控制的OSD开关的，现在呢？\"\n\nTranslation: \"I'm saying the main console UI layout, originally had PTZ and OSD separated in the motion control area, and removed OSD switches from image control area, what about now?\"\n\nSo the user is describing what was ALREADY done before (in a previous session):\n- Originally: PTZ and OSD were separated in the motion control area\n- Already done: removed OSD switches from image control area\n- Already done: added three-stage switches\n- Already done: added slow shutter function\n\nThe user is saying that the current console.html (which I have) has reverted these changes. The current version:\n- Has PTZ OSD in motion control area (line 75-80) - this seems correct\n- Has info OSD in image control area (line 320-327) - this should have been REMOVED\n- Has no slow shutter HTML element - this should exist\n- Has no three-stage switches - this should exist\n\nThe backup_20260705_205538 version has:\n- Info OSD and PTZ OSD switches (lines 84, 91) - but these might be in the image control area\n- Slow shutter HTML (line 99) ✅\n- Toggle switches (lines 83-91) ✅\n\nHmm, I think the backup_20260705_205538 might actually be the correct version. Let me check the context around lines 84-100 to see where these switches are located.\n\nActually, looking at the file sizes:\n- Current: 87741 bytes\n- backup_20260705_205538: 98047 bytes\n\nThe backup is about 10KB larger, which makes sense if it has additional features (slow shutter HTML, three-stage switches, etc.).\n\nLet me read the context around the switches in the backup to understand the layout.\n找到了！`backup_20260705_205538` (98047 bytes) 有：\n1. ✅ 慢快门 HTML 元素 (L99)\n2. ✅ 慢快门 JS 函数 (loadSlowShutter, setSlowShutter)\n3. ✅ Info OSD + PTZ OSD 开关\n4. ✅ toggle-switch 样式\n\n让我检查这个版本中开关的具体位置（是否在画面控制区域）：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_02b7215870574db183f72f2c","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":75,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/backup_20260705_205538/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_83aa5353b7a7441198780041","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && Select-String -Path \"..\\backup_20260705_205538\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"画面控制|图像控制|image.*control|v7.11\" | ForEach-Object { \"L$($_.LineNumber): $($_.Line.Trim().Substring(0, [Math]::Min(150, $_.Line.Trim().Length)))\" }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1512,"cacheRead":17590,"cacheWrite":151192,"totalTokens":170300,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783276954855,"responseId":"msg_8fdda2ad-0fe2-4217-884b-ac9afa0e0bc4"}}
