{"type":"message","id":"7b469884","parentId":"2ff1067b","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:49:20.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我看到了关键差异。让我整理一下：\n\n**备份版本 (backup_20260705_205538)**:\n- `slowShutterSelect`: ✅ HTML select 元素 + JS 引用\n- `loadSlowShutter`: ✅ 函数存在\n- `setSlowShutter`: ✅ 函数存在\n- `toggle-switch`: ✅ 样式存在\n- `infoOsdSwitch`: ✅ 在 PTZ 区域\n- `ptzOsdSwitch`: ✅ id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\"\n\n**当前版本**:\n- `slowShutterSelect`: ❌ 只有 JS 引用，没有 HTML 元素\n- `loadSlowShutter`: ❌ 不存在\n- `setSlowShutter`: ❌ 不存在\n- `toggle-switch`: ✅ 样式存在\n- `infoOsdSwitch`: ✅ 但在画面控制区域（应该在 PTZ 区域）\n- `ptzOsdSwitch`: ✅ 但 id 变成了 `ptzOsdSwitchInPtz`（备份版本是 `ptzOsdSwitch`）\n\n现在让我检查两个版本的 PTZ 区域布局差异："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_690c5ca7f1694fae80fa50f6","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":65,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/backup_20260705_205538/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_97edac75d4164de2957d9499","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":60,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":147055,"output":336,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147391,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783277350631,"responseId":"cht000d6fa6@dx19f339cf4fd29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"40de4313","parentId":"7b469884","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:49:20.909Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_690c5ca7f1694fae80fa50f6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamSub\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(2)\" title=\"子码流\">子</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamThird\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(3)\" title=\"第三码流\">三</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamStop\" onclick=\"doStopPreview()\" title=\"停止预览\">⏹</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- 预置点 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">预置点</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <select id=\"ptzPresetSelect\" style=\"padding:6px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px;min-width:100px\">\r\n                                        <option value=\"\">选择预置点</option>\r\n                                    </select>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzGotoSelectedPreset()\">前往</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzWritePreset()\">写入</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- 信息显示开关 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">信息显示</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\r\n                                        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">OSD</span>\r\n                                        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"infoOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"toggleInfoOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                        </label>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\r\n                                        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ</span>\r\n                                        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                        </label>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- v8.44: 慢快门 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">慢快门</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <select id=\"slowShutterSelect\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px;min-width:100px\" onchange=\"setSlowShutter(this.value)\">\r\n                                        <option value=\"0\">关闭</option>\r\n                                    </select>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 媒体信息(折叠,默认展开) -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"mediaLogSection\" style=\"margin-top:12px