div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\r\n                                    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                        <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                    </label>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 媒体信息(折叠,默认展开) -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"mediaLogSection\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('mediaLogSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">📡 媒体信息</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;overflow-y:auto;height:200px\" class=\"hide-scrollbar\">\r\n                                    <div id=\"mediaLogBox\" style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:monospace;color:#8b949e\">\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <!-- 中: 实时画面 + 媒体操作 -->\r\n                    <div class=\"console-center\">\r\n                        <div class=\"console-video-wrap\" style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;width:100%;\">\r\n                            <!-- v7.98: WASM 播放器占位区域,保留16:9比例 -->\r\n                            <div id=\"divPlugin\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;display:block;margin:0 auto\"></div>\r\n                            <!-- v8.10: 框选区域 overlay(默认隐藏) -->\r\n                            <div id=\"regionOverlay\" style=\"display:none;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;cursor:crosshair;z-index:100\">\r\n                                <div id=\"regionBox\" style=\"position:absolute;border:2px dashed #3fb950;background:rgba(63,185,80,0.15);display:none;pointer-events:none\"></div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 媒体操作 + 跟踪控制 并排 -->\r\n                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;width:100%\">\r\n                            <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"mediaControlSection\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('mediaControlSection')\">\r\n                                        <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3fb950;margin:0\">📷 媒体操作</h3>\r\n                                        <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px\">\r\n\n[1667 more lines in file. Use offset=120 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783277360909}}
{"type":"message","id":"6685e392","parentId":"858216fd","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:49:51.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the differences between the two versions. Let me compare the PTZ section:\n\n**Backup version (backup_20260705_205538):**\n```html\n<!-- 信息显示开关 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">信息显示</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\n        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">OSD</span>\n        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"infoOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"toggleInfoOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n        </label>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\n        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ</span>\n        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n        </label>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<!-- v8.44: 慢快门 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">慢快门</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <select id=\"slowShutterSelect\" style=\"...\" onchange=\"setSlowShutter(this.value)\">\n        <option value=\"0\">关闭</option>\n    </select>\n</div>\n```\n\n**Current version:**\n```html\n<!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\n    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n        <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n    </label>\n</div>\n```\n\nKey differences:\n1. Backup has TWO switches: infoOsdSwitch + ptzOsdSwitch\n   Current has only ONE switch: ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\n2. Backup has slowShutterSelect dropdown\n   Current is missing it\n3. Backup uses `ptzOsdSwitch` id, Current uses `ptzOsdSwitchInPtz`\n4. Backup has `<!-- 信息显示开关 -->` section title, Current has `<!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->`\n\nAlso, the backup has `ptzHome()` button in the preset section, current also has it (good).\n\nNow let me check the image control area differences - where infoOsdSwitch is in the current version:","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在情况清楚了。让我检查画面控制区域的差异：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_406f235d23544950af54dd5e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":310,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":777,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":171773,"totalTokens":172556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783277360914,"responseId":"msg_821bdec0-4d21-4439-83f7-ae5749dffa56"}}
