{"type":"message","id":"debc9f02","parentId":"6da81021","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:50:24.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the differences between the two versions:\n\n1. **Backup version (backup_20260705_205538)** - 2026 lines, 98047 bytes:\n   - Has `slowShutterSelect` HTML element with dropdown\n   - Has `loadSlowShutter` function\n   - Has `setSlowShutter` function\n   - Has `toggle-switch` styling\n   - Has `infoOsdSwitch` in the **PTZ section** (运动控制区域)\n   - Has `ptzOsdSwitch` in the **PTZ section**\n   - Info OSD and PTZ OSD are in the \"信息显示\" section in PTZ area\n\n2. **Current version** - 1785 lines, 87741 bytes:\n   - Has `slowShutterSelect` reference in JS but NO HTML element\n   - Missing `loadSlowShutter` function\n   - Missing `setSlowShutter` function\n   - Has `toggle-switch` styling\n   - Has `infoOsdSwitch` in the **画面控制区域** (image control area)\n   - Has `ptzOsdSwitchInPtz` in the PTZ section (renamed)\n   - Info OSD is separated from PTZ OSD\n\nKey differences to fix:\n1. Move infoOsdSwitch from 画面控制区域 back to PTZ区域 (alongside ptzOsdSwitch)\n2. Rename ptzOsdSwitchInPtz back to ptzOsdSwitch\n3. Add slowShutterSelect HTML element in PTZ区域\n4. Add loadSlowShutter and setSlowShutter functions\n5. Remove the infoOsdSwitch from 画面控制区域\n\nBut wait, the user also wants to keep the v8.47 feature: \"存储设备当前配置，下次连接直接套用\" - this is the save device settings functionality.\n\nLet me plan the fix:\n\n1. Backup current console.html\n2. Restore console.html from backup_20260705_205538\n3. Then add back the v8.47 restore settings functionality (if any changes are needed)\n\nActually, looking at the v8.47 changes:\n- constants.py: VERSION v8.46 → v8.47\n- whitebalance.py: Added save on completion\n- autofocus.py: Added save on completion\n- router.py: Added focus mode save, added mac_clean passing to searchers\n\nThese are all Python files, not console.html. So restoring console.html won't affect the v8.47 feature.\n\nBut wait - I need to check if console.html has any changes related to \"restore settings on connect\". Let me check the current console.html for restoreSettings functionality.\nLet me check if the current console.html has any \"restore settings\" functionality that needs to be preserved:\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cd905ee8bf6743fb8f4acca3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"restoreSettings|loadSettings|settings-saved|restore.*param\" | ForEach-Object { \"L$($_.LineNumber): $($_.Line.Trim().Substring(0, [Math]::Min(150, $_.Line.Trim().Length)))\" }"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_f71b681aa4bc47259b396d33","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\backup_20260705_205538\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"restoreSettings|loadSettings|settings-saved|restore.*param\" | ForEach-Object { \"L$($_.LineNumber): $($_.Line.Trim().Substring(0, [Math]::Min(150, $_.Line.Trim().Length)))\" }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":878,"cacheRead":167923,"cacheWrite":5298,"totalTokens":174105,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783277391905,"responseId":"msg_bd4fa016-8591-4231-9563-f09d0a894702"}}
