{"type":"message","id":"50a97e23","parentId":"c2ef76c5","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:54:30.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板，我需要继续修复。从搜索结果看：\n- 当前 console.html 已经是 backup_20260705_205538 的版本（2026行，98047 bytes）\n- 需要添加 restoreSettings 函数\n- 需要在 loadAllImageParams 后调用 restoreSettings\n\n从 read 结果看，loadAllImageParams 函数在 L856-868 左右，最后是 loadGain(deviceIp);\n\n我需要在 L868 后添加：\n1. restoreSettings 的调用（setTimeout）\n2. restoreSettings 函数的定义\n\n让我查看 loadGain 函数结束的位置，然后在那之后插入代码。\n现在我需要在 loadGain 调用后添加 restoreSettings。\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_93d60fb011314c89af673ae6","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    loadIris(deviceIp);\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    loadGain(deviceIp);\n    // v8.46: 延迟恢复保存的设置\n    setTimeout(function() { restoreSettings(deviceIp); }, 500);\n    // v7.59: 延迟结束初始化标志(等待异步加载完成)\n    setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 3000);\n}","oldText":"    loadIris(deviceIp);\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    loadGain(deviceIp);\n    // v7.59: 延迟结束初始化标志(等待异步加载完成)\n    setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 3000);\n}"}],"path":"astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":400,"cacheRead":177713,"cacheWrite":1020,"totalTokens":179139,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783277656226,"responseId":"msg_bd88137d-56c3-4f61-b428-069244d48c80"}}
{"type":"message","id":"237ea5cb","parentId":"50a97e23","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:54:30.179Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_93d60fb011314c89af673ae6","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html."}],"details":{"diff":"      ...\n  865     loadIris(deviceIp);\n  866     loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n  867     loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n  868     loadGain(deviceIp);\n+ 869     // v8.46: 延迟恢复保存的设置\n+ 870     setTimeout(function() { restoreSettings(deviceIp); }, 500);\n  869     // v7.59: 延迟结束初始化标志(等待异步加载完成)\n  870     setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 3000);\n  871 }\n  872 \n      ...","firstChangedLine":869},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783277670179}}
{"type":"message","id":"dba5ca9d","parentId":"237ea5cb","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:55:32.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add the restoreSettings function definition after the loadAllImageParams function ends. Let me find the right place to add it.\n\nThe loadAllImageParams function ends after the setTimeout calls. I need to add the restoreSettings function after that function definition.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ea37e0617c5e464eb64b543e","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"}\n\n// v8.46: 恢复设备参数记忆\nfunction restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings-saved').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data && Object.keys(r.data).length > 0) {\n            var s = r.data;\n            // 恢复曝光模式\n            if (s.exposure && s.exposure.mode) {\n                var exposureSelect = document.getElementById('exposureMode');\n                if (exposureSelect) {\n                    exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode;\n                    setExposureMode(s.exposure.mode);\n                    updateShutterIrisState();\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复快门\n            if (s.shutter && s.shutter.level) {\n                var shutterSelect = document.getElementById('shutterSpeed');\n                if (shutterSelect) {\n                    shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level;\n                    setShutterSpeed(s.shutter.level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复光圈\n            if (s.iris && s.iris.level) {\n                var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\n                if (irisSelect) {\n                    irisSelect.value = s.iris.level;\n                    setIris(s.iris.level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复白平衡\n            if (s.whitebalance) {\n                if (s.whitebalance.mode) {\n                    var wbSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n                    if (wbSelect) {\n                        wbSelect.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\n                        setWhiteBalanceMode(s.whitebalance.mode);\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复慢快门\n            if (s.slow_shutter && s.slow_shutter.dss_level) {\n                var ssSelect = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\n                if (ssSelect) {\n                    ssSelect.value = s.slow_shutter.dss_level;\n                    onSlowShutterChange(s.slow_shutter.dss_level);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        console.warn('[RESTORE] 恢复设置失败:', e);\n    });\n}\n\n// v7.32: 显示功能检测覆盖层","oldText":"}\n\n// v7.32: 显示功能检测覆盖层"}],"path":"astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":644,"cacheRead":177713,"cacheWrite":1446,"totalTokens":179809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783277670183,"responseId":"msg_6e76972f-c6a6-4083-8dec-2d66cf345a80"}}
