{"type":"message","id":"21fd6fed","parentId":"eec598ac","timestamp":"2026-07-05T18:57:40.540Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see there's an encoding error in the script I wrote. The issue is with the Unicode characters (checkmark symbols) being printed to stdout in a GBK environment.\n\nI need to fix the script to either:\n1. Use ASCII-safe characters instead of Unicode\n2. Handle the encoding properly\n\nLet me rewrite the script with ASCII characters.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，编码错误。我重写脚本，使用纯ASCII字符：\nThe issue is Unicode characters in the print statement causing encoding errors. Let me rewrite with ASCII-safe characters:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_dfb1a4f5a7f341ae987b2449","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Playwright screenshot verification - v8.48\"\"\"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport time\n\nurl = \"http://127.0.0.1:10280/console\"\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n    page = browser.new_page(viewport={\"width\": 1920, \"height\": 1080})\n    \n    print(f\"Visiting: {url}\")\n    page.goto(url, wait_until=\"networkidle\")\n    time.sleep(2)\n    \n    # Screenshot full page\n    page.screenshot(path=\"console_v848_full.png\", full_page=True)\n    print(\"[OK] Saved: console_v848_full.png\")\n    \n    # Check key elements\n    elements = [\n        (\"slowShutterSelect\", \"Slow shutter select\"),\n        (\"infoOsdSwitch\", \"Info OSD switch\"),\n        (\"ptzOsdSwitch\", \"PTZ OSD switch\"),\n    ]\n    \n    print(\"\\nFeature check:\")\n    for elem_id, desc in elements:\n        elem = page.query_selector(f\"#{elem_id}\")\n        status = \"[OK]\" if elem else \"[FAIL]\"\n        print(f\"  {status} {desc}\")\n    \n    # Check restoreSettings function\n    has_func = page.evaluate(\"typeof restoreSettings !== 'undefined'\")\n    status = \"[OK]\" if has_func else \"[FAIL]\"\n    print(f\"  {status} restoreSettings function\")\n    \n    browser.close()\n    print(\"\\n[OK] Screenshot verification complete\")\n","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/screenshot_v848.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":523,"cacheRead":179969,"cacheWrite":3258,"totalTokens":183756,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783277844675,"responseId":"msg_03a0f75d-fbb7-4e84-a7c7-8625aa6cb5b1"}}
