{"type":"message","id":"228b0c4f","parentId":"c35d347d","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:02:21.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still all FAIL. Let me check what's actually on the page - maybe there's a login page or redirect. Let me look at the screenshot or check the actual HTML content.\n\nActually, let me check the screenshot to see what's on the page, or let me modify the script to get the page content.\n\nLet me check if the console page requires authentication or if there's something blocking it.\n\nActually, let me read the screenshot to see what's on the page.\n还是全部 FAIL。让我检查页面实际内容：\nStill all FAIL. Let me check the actual page content:\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ed28b73c9eaa40bfac2e5200","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && python -c \"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport time\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n    page = browser.new_page(viewport={'width': 1920, 'height': 1080})\n    page.goto('http://127.0.0.1:10280/console', wait_until='networkidle')\n    time.sleep(3)\n    \n    # Get page title and URL\n    print('Page title:', page.title())\n    print('Page URL:', page.url)\n    \n    # Check if there's a login form or redirect\n    login_form = page.query_selector('form')\n    if login_form:\n        print('Login form detected!')\n    \n    # Get all input elements\n    inputs = page.query_selector_all('input')\n    print(f'Input elements: {len(inputs)}')\n    \n    # Get all select elements\n    selects = page.query_selector_all('select')\n    print(f'Select elements: {len(selects)}')\n    \n    # Get page HTML length\n    html = page.content()\n    print(f'HTML length: {len(html)} chars')\n    \n    # Check if slowShutterSelect exists in HTML\n    if 'slowShutterSelect' in html:\n        print('slowShutterSelect found in HTML')\n    else:\n        print('slowShutterSelect NOT in HTML')\n    \n    if 'infoOsdSwitch' in html:\n        print('infoOsdSwitch found in HTML')\n    else:\n        print('infoOsdSwitch NOT in HTML')\n    \n    browser.close()\n\"\n"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe features are all failing. This means the page is not loading the updated console.html properly, or there's a caching issue, or the page is not rendering correctly.\n\nLet me check:\n1. Is the page actually loading the updated console.html?\n2. Is there a caching issue?\n3. Let me check the actual HTML of the page\n\nThe screenshot was saved. Let me look at it. Also, let me check if the console.html was properly updated.\n\nActually, wait - I replaced the console.html file, but the running AstroHub might be using the old file because Python might have cached it. Let me verify the file was actually replaced.\n\nAlso, I should check if the page is loading at all - maybe it's showing a login page or error page.\n\nLet me:\n1. Check the screenshot\n2. Verify the console.html file was replaced\n3. Check if there's a caching issue功能检查全失败了。让我检查页面实际加载的内容：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_02ca7331807441b1a06da0b8","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":95,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":796,"cacheRead":185442,"cacheWrite":358,"totalTokens":186602,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783278100236,"responseId":"msg_030ef264-50d0-4c22-b346-d53fc05a1912"}}
