{"type":"message","id":"e277e1b5","parentId":"66e363f3","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:06:33.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The screenshot shows the AstroHub dashboard/index page, not the console page. The page shows the dashboard view with system logs, PTZ devices, video streams, etc. I need to navigate to the console page specifically.\n\nLooking at the top navigation bar, I can see tabs:\n- 仪表盘 (Dashboard - currently active)\n- 设备管理\n- 主控台 (Console)\n- 观测计划\n- 高级功能\n- 回放\n- 设置\n\nSo I need to click on \"主控台\" (Console) tab to see the console page with the slow shutter, OSD switches, etc.\n\nAlso, the page shows no device is connected (PTZ设备: 0, ASCOM: 未连接). The console page might not show the controls without a connected device.\n\nLet me take another screenshot after clicking on the console tab.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"这是仪表盘页面，不是主控台。需要点击\"主控台\"标签。让我导航到主控台页面截图：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_946ed4cd2a7240e6b6597f1f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Playwright screenshot - navigate to console tab\"\"\"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport time\n\nurl = \"http://127.0.0.1:10280/\"\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n    page = browser.new_page(viewport={\"width\": 1920, \"height\": 1080})\n    \n    print(f\"Visiting: {url}\")\n    page.goto(url, wait_until=\"networkidle\")\n    time.sleep(2)\n    \n    # Click console tab (主控台)\n    console_tab = page.query_selector(\"text=主控台\")\n    if console_tab:\n        console_tab.click()\n        print(\"[OK] Clicked console tab\")\n        time.sleep(3)\n    else:\n        print(\"[WARN] Console tab not found, trying alt selector\")\n        # Try finding by nav link\n        nav = page.query_selector(\"nav a:nth-child(3)\")\n        if nav:\n            nav.click()\n            time.sleep(3)\n    \n    # Screenshot console page\n    page.screenshot(path=\"console_v848_page.png\", full_page=True)\n    print(\"[OK] Saved: console_v848_page.png\")\n    \n    # Feature checks on console page\n    checks = [\n        (\"slowShutterSelect\", \"Slow shutter select\"),\n        (\"infoOsdSwitch\", \"Info OSD switch\"),\n        (\"ptzOsdSwitch\", \"PTZ OSD switch\"),\n    ]\n    \n    print(\"\\nConsole page features:\")\n    for elem_id, desc in checks:\n        elem = page.query_selector(f\"#{elem_id}\")\n        status = \"[OK]\" if elem else \"[FAIL]\"\n        print(f\"  {status} {desc}\")\n    \n    # Check if \"信息显示\" section exists (backup_20260705_205538 layout)\n    info_section = page.query_selector(\"text=信息显示\")\n    status = \"[OK]\" if info_section else \"[FAIL]\"\n    print(f\"  {status} Info display section\")\n    \n    # Check if \"慢快门\" label exists\n    ss_label = page.query_selector(\"text=慢快门\")\n    status = \"[OK]\" if ss_label else \"[FAIL]\"\n    print(f\"  {status} Slow shutter label\")\n    \n    browser.close()\n    print(\"\\n[OK] Done\")\n","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/screenshot_v848.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d550be33c454473282c7ff30","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && python screenshot_v848.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":837,"cacheRead":17590,"cacheWrite":176281,"totalTokens":194714,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783278366881,"responseId":"msg_2aebcc10-2967-4f7f-9255-43399a7909cd"}}
