{"type":"message","id":"30302095","parentId":"7f30f5c1","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:10:49.486Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_2e0754aabd934b54a96524c0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"L3267: @api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"��ȡ��������\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nL3268: async def get_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\nL3286: resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\r\nL3312: supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\nL3326: supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\nL3374: opt_values = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\nL3769: @api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"��ȡ����������\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nL3770: async def get_slow_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":449,"aggregated":"L3267: @api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"��ȡ��������\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nL3268: async def get_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\nL3286: resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\r\nL3312: supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\nL3326: supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\nL3374: opt_values = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\nL3769: @api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"��ȡ����������\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nL3770: async def get_slow_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783278649486}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a846b09","parentId":"30302095","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:11:01.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板问的是运动控制区域（左侧）的快门速度是怎么得到的。\n\n从搜索结果可以看到：\n\n1. **运动控制区域显示**：\n   - 截图中左侧有：`快门: 1/25`\n   - 对应的 HTML 元素是 `id=\"ptzShutter\"`，显示在 `class=\"info-value\"` 中\n\n2. **获取来源**：\n   - `loadShutter(deviceIp)` 函数从设备获取快门值\n   - API 端点：`/api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter` → `GET /ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Shutter`\n   - 返回的值填充到 `shutterSpeed` 下拉菜单（画面控制区域）\n\n3. **运动控制区域 vs 画面控制区域**：\n   - 运动控制区域：`id=\"ptzShutter\"` 显示当前快门速度\n   - 画面控制区域：`id=\"shutterSpeed\"` 下拉菜单选择快门速度\n\n4. **关键问题**：运动控制区域的 `ptzShutter` 元素是从哪里更新的？\n\n让我检查 `loadShutter` 函数中是否更新了 `ptzShutter` 元素。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"从截图可见，运动控制区域（左侧）显示 **快门: 1/25**，对应元素 `id=\"ptzShutter\"`。让我确认这个值的来源：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:122","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1010,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":77482,"output":325,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77807,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783278649490,"responseId":"cht000de794@dx19f33b0c9b229bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5958b18b","parentId":"2a846b09","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:11:01.922Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:122","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    var btnOn = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOn');\r\n    var btnOff = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOff');\r\n    if (btnOn && btnOff) {\r\n        if (enabled) {\r\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\r\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\r\n        } else {\r\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\r\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    // 同步运动控制区的 PTZ OSD 开关\r\n    var sw = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitch');\r\n    if (sw) sw.checked = enabled;\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled) {\r\n    var btnOn = document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOn');\r\n    var btnOff = document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOff');\r\n    if (btnOn && btnOff) {\r\n        if (enabled) {\r\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\r\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\r\n        } else {\r\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\r\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    // v6.14: 同步开关状态\r\n    var sw = document.getElementById('infoOsdSwitch');\r\n    if (sw) sw.checked = enabled;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 加载白平衡\r\nfunction loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/whitebalance').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n            var wb = r.data;\r\n            deviceImageParams.whiteBalance = wb;\r\n\r\n            var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbModeSelect) {\r\n                // 根据设备返回的模式设置下拉菜单\r\n                if (wb.mode === 'manual') {\r\n                    wbModeSelect.value = 'manual';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    wbModeSelect.value = 'auto';\r\n                }\r\n                // 触发显示/隐藏逻辑\r\n                onWbModeChange(wbModeSelect.value);\r\n\n[1024 more lines in file. Use offset=1060 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783278661922}}
