{"type":"message","id":"92d32be8","parentId":"74ba1654","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:21:10.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to do a retrospective (复盘) and update memory. Let me properly update the HEARTBEAT.md with the new v8.47 and v8.48 sections, and add the new errors to .learnings/ERRORS.md.\n\nLooking at the file structure, ERRORS.md already has content up to the v7.115 retrospective. I need to append new error records at the end.\n\nLet me write the updated memory properly. I need to:\n1. Append v8.47 and v8.48 to HEARTBEAT.md (already done with the first edit)\n2. Append new error records to .learnings/ERRORS.md\n3. Update memory/2026-07-06.md\n\nFor ERRORS.md, I need to find the end of the file and append. The current structure ends with \"备份：backup_20260628_dedup/\". I need to add new sections after that.\n\nActually, looking at the file, it seems the structure is:\n```\n# 复盘：v7.109 → v7.111 录制功能灾难\n...\n# 复盘：v7.115 去冗余\n...\n```\n\nSo I can just append to the end. But the edit tool is failing because it's trying to replace specific text. Let me use write with append mode... actually write doesn't support append. Let me use edit with the exact text at the end.\n\nActually, let me just read the end of the file to see what the last lines are.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me read the end of ERRORS.md to append the new errors properly."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:296","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":180,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/.learnings/ERRORS.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user wants me to complete the retrospective and update memory. Let me check the current state of the files.\n\nI need to:\n1. Read the end of ERRORS.md to append new error records\n2. Complete updating HEARTBEAT.md\n3. Update memory/2026-07-06.md\n\nLet me continue from where I left off.</think>Let me read the end of ERRORS.md to append the new errors:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:297","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":170,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/.learnings/ERRORS.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"Now I can see the end of ERRORS.md. Let me append the new error records at the end.</think>"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:298","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"---\n\n# 复盘：v8.47-v8.48 console.html 恢复灾难\n\n**日期**: 2026-07-06\n**任务**: 设备参数记忆功能 + console.html UI 修复\n**结果**: 6 次迭代才稳定，犯多个严重错误\n\n---\n\n## 我犯了什么错\n\n### 1. 修改 console.html 时覆盖现有功能（最严重）\n\n修改了 console.html 的 restoreSettings 功能，但不小心覆盖了：\n1. 慢快门 HTML 元素（slowShutterSelect）\n2. OSD 开关位置（Info OSD 被移到画面控制区）\n\n**根因**：\n- 没有先检查 console.html 的现有功能\n- 没有先备份 console.html\n- 假设修改不会影响现有功能\n\n**教训**：\n- 修改前必须备份\n- 修改前必须检查现有功能\n- 修改后必须用 Playwright 截图验证\n\n---\n\n### 2. 备份不完整导致恢复困难\n\n备份_20260706_0032 只有 5 个文件（autofocus.py, constants.py, device_settings.py, router.py, whitebalance.py），缺少 console.html。\n\n**根因**：\n- 备份时没有包含所有可能受影响的文件\n- 没有意识到 console.html 也会受影响\n\n**教训**：\n- 备份时要包含所有可能受影响的文件\n- 特别是前端 HTML/JS 文件\n\n---\n\n### 3. 没有先对比再修改\n\n修改前没有对比当前版本和备份版本的差异，导致覆盖了已有功能。\n\n**根因**：\n- 没有养成对比差异的习惯\n- 认为只是小修改，不会覆盖\n\n**教训**：\n- 修改前先对比差异\n- 特别是恢复备份时，先确认备份版本的功能完整性\n\n---\n\n## 正确做法总结\n\n| 场景 | 正确做法 |\n|------|----------|\\| 修改前端文件 | 先备份，再对比差异，最后修改 |\n| 恢复备份 | 先确认备份版本功能完整，再恢复 |\n| 添加新功能 | 先检查是否影响现有功能 |\n| 修改后验证 | 用 Playwright 截图验证所有功能 |\n\n---\n\n## 涉及文件\n\n- `astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html` — 从 backup_20260705_205538 恢复 + 添加 restoreSettings\n- `astrohub/src/controlpanel/whitebalance.py` — 添加 mac_clean 参数 + save_settings\n- `astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py` — 添加 mac_clean 参数 + save_settings\n- `astrohub/src/api/router.py` — 添加 focus 模式保存 + mac_clean 传递\n- `astrohub/src/main/constants.py` — VERSION v8.46→v8.48\n- 备份：`backup_20260706_0129/`、`backup_20260706_0252/`","oldText":"---\n\n# 复盘：v7.115 去冗余 — 双 PTZController 类 + 过度开发遗留\n\n**日期**: 2026-06-28\n**任务**: 统一预置点设置方法 + 删除 opencode 分叉副本\n**结果**: 删除 ~320 行冗余代码，E2E 双通过\n\n---\n\n## 我犯了什么错\n\n### 1. Stop-Process -Name python -Force 无差别杀进程（最严重）\n\n执行了 3 次 `Get-Process -Name python | Stop-Process -Force`。\n这会杀掉所有 python.exe，可能误杀网关进程。违反铁律。\n\n**正确做法**：按端口号精确定位\n```powershell\n$pid = (Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 10280).OwningProcess\nif ($pid) { Stop-Process -Id $pid -Force }\n```\n\n### 2. 删函数时误删了路由端点\n\n用 `_fix_router.py` 删除 `_setup_home_preset` 函数定义时，\n把紧随其后的 `@api_router.post(\"/advanced/detect/start\")` 也删了。\n因为两个代码块紧挨着，`find` 匹配范围过大。\n\n**修复**：从备份恢复 router.py，重新精确替换。\n\n### 3. Windows pwsh 多行字符串问题\n\n在 `python -c` 中用 `'''...'''` 多行字符串，超过2行就报 SyntaxError。\n浪费多次尝试。\n\n**正确做法**：用 `write` 工具创建独立 `.py` 脚本执行。\n\n---\n\n## 正确做法总结\n\n| 场景 | 正确做法 |\n|------|----------|\n| 杀进程 | 按端口号定位，不用进程名 |\n| 删除代码块 | 先备份，精确匹配边界，验证编译 |\n| 复杂字符串操作 | 写独立 .py 脚本，不塞进 -c |\n| 循环导入 | 删 __init__.py 中不必要的 re-export |\n\n---\n\n## 涉及文件\n\n- `src/core/ptz_controller.py` — 删除 PTZController 副本(-310行)，import 正版\n- `src/ptz/isapi/ptz.py` — 迁移 focus_move_continuous + focus_stop\n- `src/ptz/__init__.py` — 删除循环导入\n- `src/ptz/core/__init__.py` — 删除循环导入\n- `src/advanced/function.py` — 顶部统一 import\n- `src/api/router.py` — 顶部统一 import\n- 备份：`backup_20260628_dedup/`"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/.learnings/ERRORS.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user is asking me to complete the retrospective (复盘) and update memory. Let me check what still needs to be done:\n\n1. HEARTBEAT.md - Already updated with v8.47 and v8.48 sections\n2. memory/2026-07-06.md - Already updated\n3. .learnings/ERRORS.md - Need to append new error records\n\nThe edit failed because the old text doesn't match exactly. Let me use a different approach - I'll read the end of the file and append the new content.\n\nActually, let me just try a simpler approach - find the exact text to replace. The issue is that the old text includes a lot of content that's already in the file. Let me try to match just the end of the file.\n\nActually, the better approach is to