*：\n- 备份时要包含所有可能受影响的文件\n- 特别是前端 HTML/JS 文件\n\n---\n\n### 3. 没有先对比再修改\n\n修改前没有对比当前版本和备份版本的差异，导致覆盖了已有功能。\n\n**根因**：\n- 没有养成对比差异的习惯\n- 认为只是小修改，不会覆盖\n\n**教训**：\n- 修改前先对比差异\n- 特别是恢复备份时，先确认备份版本的功能完整性\n\n---\n\n## 正确做法总结\n\n| 场景 | 正确做法 |\n|------|----------|\n| 修改前端文件 | 先备份，再对比差异，最后修改 |\n| 恢复备份 | 先确认备份版本功能完整，再恢复 |\n| 添加新功能 | 先检查是否影响现有功能 |\n| 修改后验证 | 用 Playwright 截图验证所有功能 |\n\n---\n\n## 涉及文件\n\n- `astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html` — 从 backup_20260705_205538 恢复 + 添加 restoreSettings\n- `astrohub/src/controlpanel/whitebalance.py` — 添加 mac_clean 参数 + save_settings\n- `astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py` — 添加 mac_clean 参数 + save_settings\n- `astrohub/src/api/router.py` — 添加 focus 模式保存 + mac_clean 传递\n- `astrohub/src/main/constants.py` — VERSION v8.46→v8.48\n- 备份：`backup_20260706_0129/`、`backup_20260706_0252/`","oldText":"- 备份：`backup_20260628_dedup/`"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/.learnings/ERRORS.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user wants me to complete the retrospective and update memory. I've been trying to edit ERRORS.md but the edit is failing. Let me try a different approach - I'll write a new file with all the content from the existing ERRORS.md plus the new content.\n\nActually, let me first check what the current state is and then provide a comprehensive summary to the user. The key thing is that the user asked for \"复盘，更新记忆\" - a retrospective and memory update.\n\nLet me verify what was successfully updated and what still needs work.</think>Let me check the current state of the files to see what was successfully updated."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:302","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && Get-Content ..\\HEARTBEAT.md | Select-String \"v8.4[678]|v8.48|v8.47\" | Select-Object -First 10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:303","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub && Get-Content ..\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md | Select-String \"v8.47|v8.48|console.html\" | Select-Object -First 10"}},{"type":"